body: |2-
  Fewer columns, more rows.
  The unit is more complex: person-year.

  | person | year | spinach_boost_strength |
  | Alice  | 2024 |                     90 |
  | Alice  | 2025 |                     93 |
  | Bob    | 2024 |                     78 |
  | Bob    | 2025 |                     81 |
